{"tid":1631194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲記唔記得天琦同我地講過d咩","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:10:13.000Z","uid":41412,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ead53864337c1166d3e8ad2f10c90cc94f0466","tid":1631194,"uid":41412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你地唔好做，係要諗清楚點樣做。根本有好多手足係比情緒主導左個行為，加上連登各種一毛帶風向。 <br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得以前高登有一句說話，上高登，勿認真。保持自已的獨立思考係呢場運動好重要既動作。"},{"pid":"de0b546e640d40f4bb35547306f59d25c55688cb","tid":1631194,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79ddd21131546682d96a470d58245760cfe4e54f","tid":1631194,"uid":41412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9340c704dc55f4b76d045800ade1950d24a1d92a","tid":1631194,"uid":41412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b7d2225fea92ccbcc19fcb700008b1e2d20fbb2","tid":1631194,"uid":41412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}